      {
        "id": "797bca3e689f7ebedbadd2f73b33f337454d3cdf",
        "author": {
          "account_id": 33,
          "name": "James Forsyth",
          "display_name": null,
          "email": "jf2512@att.com",
          "username": "jimmydot"
        },
        "author_role": "REVIEWER",
        "timestamp": "2017-09-12 12:40:23.000000000",
        "message": "Patch Set 8:\n\nWhat's the status on this one?  Will network-services be removed from the schema per our discussion last week?",
        "patchset_number": 8
      },
      {
        "id": "c0f52f9ee94ab95b6e308a87335c6fa98ffa11e6",
        "author": {
          "account_id": 39,
          "name": "Weitao Gao",
          "display_name": null,
          "email": "victor.gao@huawei.com",
          "username": "g310497"
        },
        "author_role": "REVIEWER",
        "timestamp": "2017-09-12 13:54:54.000000000",
        "message": "Patch Set 8:\n\n> What's the status on this one?  Will network-services be removed\n > from the schema per our discussion last week?\n\nAs we discussed last week?Subhash, i think we could re-use service instance instead of adding network-service node",
        "patchset_number": 8
      },
      {
        "id": "fa2ee9ef7837b7c5b014bc0847ac14268e754437",
        "author": {
          "account_id": 141,
          "name": "maopeng zhang",
          "display_name": null,
          "email": "zhang.maopeng1@zte.com.cn",
          "username": "maopengzhang"
        },
        "author_role": "REVIEWER",
        "timestamp": "2017-09-14 14:19:26.000000000",
        "message": "Patch Set 8:\n\nNetwork Service is a concept from ETSI IFA. It is composed of VNFs, VL and VNFFG(Future) resources. In the VoLTE case, there is E2E service, which is composed of EPC network service and IMS network service in NFV domain, and underlay/overlay VPN in the SDN domain. Network service's attributes are different from E2E service or service from the openECOMP.\nIf support the two layer services in AAI, it will more clear for the code.",
        "patchset_number": 8
      },
      {
        "id": "36f708d83e648d6a8a48a2a5ada3212e208408ba",
        "author": {
          "account_id": 33,
