          "username": "maopengzhang"
        },
        "author_role": "REVIEWER",
        "timestamp": "2017-09-25 12:12:31.000000000",
        "message": "Patch Set 8:\n\n@subhash kumar singh, in R1, the SDC support E2E service and Network service both via service, and use service catagory to identify the different services. The two different services can have different properties, and inputs, and topology as well.",
        "patchset_number": 8
      },
